# 08 - Meeting Notes Processor
# Transform raw notes into actionable summaries

NAME meeting-processor
INPUT notes_file

GOAL read_notes "Read the meeting notes from $notes_file using the read tool."
GOAL extract "Extract: decisions made, action items (with owners if mentioned), open questions, and key discussion points."
GOAL format "Format into a clean summary with sections: Summary, Decisions, Action Items, Open Questions, Next Steps."
GOAL save "Write the processed notes to a new file with '-processed' suffix using write tool."

RUN process USING read_notes, extract, format, save
